    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/25d95616c5c3594b9b9d7f682b797b8e.webp?t=1768922106\" width=300 height=58 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/02a3b8c31b51170d373020c29efb71a5.poster.avif?t=1768922106\" width=614 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/02a3b8c31b51170d373020c29efb71a5.webm?t=1768922106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/02a3b8c31b51170d373020c29efb71a5.mp4?t=1768922106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The dragon snatched the princess, and the tsar commands you to undertake a mission from which none have returned. Ahead lie forests, swamps, and fairy-tale creatures that may either aid or deceive you. Fight for the princess, flee, or uncover the dragon’s hidden secret? The choice is yours—but brace yourself for the unexpected!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/ce39a58b8bdd0c1967e22a75fdeff5f8.webp?t=1768922106\" width=300 height=58 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/4e2b388b51c75d2f362d5387c269402b.poster.avif?t=1768922106\" width=614 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/4e2b388b51c75d2f362d5387c269402b.webm?t=1768922106\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3254800/extras/4e2b388b51c75d2f362d5387c269402b.mp4?t=1768922106\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every situation is a scene with two cards. Help push the cart or deceive the guards? Choose, test the outcome, and don’t be surprised if you end up in the bushes instead of performing a heroic deed. Paths branch, endings vary, and death is just a reason to start anew. Prove you can handle this!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
